		<title>DURBAN&#8217;S NEW TAXI INITIATIVE GOES LIVE</title>
		<link>https://www.newspages.co.za/durbans-new-taxi-initiative-goes-live/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 13 Nov 2018 10:18:29 +0000</pubDate>
